```mermaid
flowchart TD

A([Start Rental Activity Interview])

A --> B["📋 1. Tell me about your rental property
• Residential, commercial, vacation?
• Rented all year?
• How many properties?"]

B --> C["👤 2. Who manages the property?
• You?
• Property manager?
• Shared responsibilities?"]

C --> D["🛠️ 3. What did YOU personally do?
• Advertise property
• Screen tenants
• Collect rent
• Coordinate repairs
• Communicate with tenants
• Maintain records"]

D --> E["⏱️ 4. Approximately how much time did you spend?
• Estimated hours
• More than anyone else?
• Did others perform most of the work?"]

E --> F["📑 5. Did you make management decisions?
• Approve tenants
• Set rental rates
• Authorize repairs
• Decide improvements"]

F --> G{"Active Participation?"}

G -->|Likely Yes| H["Consider $25,000 Special Allowance"]

G -->|Need More Analysis| I["Evaluate Material Participation"]

I --> J["👥 6. Who else participated?
• Property manager
• Spouse
• Contractors
• Other owners"]

J --> K["🏢 7. Is real estate your primary profession?
• Real property trade/business?
• 750+ hours?
• More than half of working time?"]

K --> L{"Real Estate Professional?"}

L -->|Yes| M["Apply Material Participation Tests"]

L -->|No| N["Rental generally remains Passive"]

M --> O["Determine whether rental activity is Passive or Nonpassive"]

N --> P["Review Passive Loss Rules & Carryforwards"]

O --> Q([Complete Tax Analysis])
P --> Q
```
